Task 1 - WebHosting

Step 1

Launch Instance - centos
 - Security Group (SSH, HTTP)

 Step 2 

 Connect to instance through Gitbash
 - Install HTTPD and Git
   sudo yum -y install httpd git
   sudo systemctl start httpd
   sudo systemctl enable httpd

Step 3 
- Add content to /var/www/html
  sudo git clone https://github.com/lvchiney/ecomm.git /var/www/html
  sudo systemctl restart httpd
  Now the website would be up and running.
  